<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Lotus Rose Counseling"
  description="Terms of service for Lotus Rose Counseling website in Orem, Utah."
>

  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-container">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: March 24, 2026</p>

        <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using the Lotus Rose Counseling website (lotusrosecounseling.com), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our website.</p>

